Name: Rina
Desc: Use it to obtain the Agent or unlock the Agent's Mindscapes.
Desc2:
Snapshots from Rina's daily life and from in combat, recording important moments before and after she became an Agent.
These images also provide insights into her fighting style and favorite weapons, helping to better understand her strengths.

There's a smiling emoji drawn on the back, which looks like some kind of friendly greeting... Only looks like.
